<span class="boss">Lyngbakr</span>:<br>
<ul><br>
<li><span class="ability">Sonic Bloop</span>: 🛡️ <span class="mechanic">Moderate tank buster</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Upsweep</span>: 💥 <span class="mechanic">Party-wide damage, triggers crystal AoEs</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Tidal Breath</span>: 🏃 <span class="mechanic">Get behind boss to avoid wide frontal AoE</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Body Slam</span>: 💥 <span class="mechanic">Party-wide damage, spawns crystals of various sizes</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Floodstide</span>: 🎯 <span class="mechanic">Light damage AoE markers on all players</span></li><br>
</ul><br>
