<span class="boss">Arkas</span>:<br>
<ul><br>
<li><span class="ability">Battle Cry</span>: 💥 <span class="mechanic">Party-wide damage, limits arena on 2nd cast</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Lightning Leap</span>: 🔴 <span class="mechanic">Boss leaps away from tank, circular AoE + lightning lines</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Ripper Claw</span>: 🛡️ <span class="mechanic">Moderate tank buster</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Spinning Claw</span>: 🔴 <span class="mechanic">Circular AoE + wider lightning lines across arena</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Lightning Rampage</span>: 🏃 <span class="mechanic">Boss jumps 4 times, each with circular AoE + lightning lines</span></li><br>
