<span class="boss">Octomammoth</span>:<br>
<ul><br>
<li><span class="mechanic">Accompanied by 8 untargetable Tentacles that will attack independently. Irregular arena with 5 circular platforms connected by bridges</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Tidal Roar</span>: 💥 <span class="mechanic">Low party-wide damage</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Octostroke</span>: 📐 <span class="mechanic">4 platforms flanked by tentacles' cone AoEs</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Vivid Eyes</span>: ➡️⬅️ <span class="mechanic">Narrow AoE through center, stand close to boss or far</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Saline Spit</span>: 🔴 <span class="mechanic">Circle AoEs on platforms, stand on connectors</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Tidal Breath</span>: 📐 <span class="mechanic">Wide frontal AoE, boss turns leaving 1.5 platforms safe</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Telekinesis</span>: 🔗 <span class="mechanic">Crystals tethered to platforms, become circle AoEs</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Breathstroke</span>: 📐 <span class="mechanic">Octostroke + Tidal Breath, 1 tentacle on safe platform</span></li><br>
<li><span class="ability">Water Drop</span>: 🎯 <span class="mechanic">Spread to avoid overlapping circle AoEs on players</span></li><br>
</ul><br>
